NAME
    Log::ger::Output::Syslog - Send logs to syslog

VERSION
    version 0.005

SYNOPSIS
     use Log::ger::Output 'Syslog' => (
         ident    => 'myprog', # required
         facility => 'daemon', # optional, default 'user'
     );
     use Log::ger;

     log_warn "blah ...";

DESCRIPTION
    This output plugin sends logs to syslog using Sys::Syslog. It accepts
    all syslog(3) facilities.

CONFIGURATION
  ident
  facility
  logopt
SEE ALSO
    Log::ger

    Sys::Syslog

AUTHOR
